SUMMARY:The Non-Human & Agentic AI Identity Summit (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:The identity landscape has already shifted.\nNon-human identiti
 es vastly outnumber human ones\, and the rapid rise of Agentic AI is trans
 forming these identities from passive\, deterministic processes into auton
 omous digital actors\, capable of making decisions and initiating actions 
 at machine speed.\nAs organizations deploy AI agents that operate with lim
 ited human oversight\, traditional IAM\, security\, and governance models 
 are being pushed beyond their original design. The results: A fast-growing
 \, largely ungoverned attack surface Access that is routinely over-privile
 ged Unclear accountability\, and Existing controls that are poorly matched
  to identities that can replicate\, reason\, and act independently.\n\nDet
 ails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/non-human-identity-agentic-ai-summit/\
 n\nSpeakers: Lalit Choda (Founder • Non-Human Identity Management Group)
  | Eve Maler (President/Founder • Venn Factory) | Rogério Rondini (Prin
 cipal Identity Solution Architect • PwC) | Niv Goldenberg (CPO • Linx 
 Security) | Steven Rennick (Senior Leader\, IT Architecture • Ciena) | T
 roy Wilkinson (Global CISO • Between roles) | Amir Ofek (Co-Founder & CE
 O • aizome) | Andrej Safundzic (CEO • Lumos) | Itamar Apelblat (Co-Fou
 nder & CEO • Token Security) | Alexis Moyse (Co-Founder & CEO • Clarit
 y Security) | Homayun Yaqub (Vice President of Advisory Services • Digit
 al Hands) | Rahul Godha (Staff Software Engineer • LinkedIn) | Renee Gut
 tman (Founder & Principal • Cisohive & Former CISO of Campbell Soup\, Ro
 yal Caribbean & The Coca-Cola Company) | David Chan (• University of Sou
 thern California) | Elisa Abedrapo (IAM leader and Practitioner • I repr
 esent myself) | Don D'Souza (Director of Cybersecurity (IAM) • Fannie Ma
 e) | Sriram Santhanam (Chief Cyber Officer • Human Managed) | Murad Dike
 idek (Head of Cybersecurity • University of Illinois Hospital & Health S
 ciences System) | Ross Sherman (Sr. Director\, Global Agentic AI • SailP
 oint) | Henrique Teixeira (SVP of Strategy • Saviynt) | Shashwat Sehgal 
 (Co-Founder and CEO • P0 Security) | David Goldschlag (Co-Founder and CE
 O • Aembit) | Jesse Minor (Identity Security Specialist • KPMG) | Amit
  Masand (CEO • IDMEXPRESS) | Ashay Raut (Principal Engineer • Amazon) 
 | Devan D’Silva (Solution Engineering Manager • SailPoint)\n\nSession 
 Type: WORKSHOP\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Mandalay Bay I
