SUMMARY:Introduction to Identity (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:You may be newly thrown into the multiverse of identity / acces
 s management\, or you may have been part of it for so long that you either
  got dizzy or turned cynical.\nIn either case\, this introduction to the f
 ield will set you on a straight path to redemption and acceptance into the
  inner ranks of identity professionals. Or more precisely and importantly\
 , it will help you take part in conversations about access and digital ide
 ntity\, which should help your conference experience as well as your furth
 er career.\nWe will review the foundations of access and then identity\, l
 ook at the different sub-groups making up IAM\, attempt to explain and ill
 ustrate most of them\, and place them in a wider context.\n\nDetails: http
 s://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=3931782\n\nSpeakers: Espen Bago (
 Head of IAM • Gritera Security / IdentiBeer) | Lance Peterman (Lead Engi
 neer - CyberSecurity Engineering • Dick's Sporting Goods)\n\nSession Typ
 e: MASTERCLASS\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Mandalay Bay I
