  digital identity professionals is more important than ever\, but the scal
 e and the nature of our craft must evolve. Join Andrew Hindle as he explor
 es how the industry and the profession of Identity can and must develop\, 
 whilst staying true to its fundamentals. Our work starts now!\n\nDetails: 
 https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=3961697\n\nSpeakers: Andi Hin
