SUMMARY:The Craft of Leadership: Innovation into Action with Sue Gordon (PD
 T)
DESCRIPTION:Sue Gordon argues leadership is not a born trait\, but a craft 
 that can be learned and refined. Gordon draws on her 30 years of experienc
 e at every level of the intelligence community to provide not only an acti
 onable framework for becoming an effective leader but also to inspire secu
 rity teams to lead through change and innovation. Gordon will explore key 
 leadership principles\, such as courage\, self-awareness\, resilience\, an
 d effective decision-making\, necessary to leap into uncertainty\, challen
 ge the status quo\, and maximize one’s success as a leader.\n\nDetails: 
 https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=3985223\n\nSpeakers: Sue Gord
 on (Transformative Leader & Disruptive Technologies Expert company: Former
  Top-Ranking National Intelligence & National Security Official • Nation
 al Security Agency)\n\nSession Type: KEYNOTE\n\nAll times are in Pacific D
 aylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
