BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:identiverse-2026-event-4009748@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260615T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260615T180000
SUMMARY:Navigating the Identity Revolution in Real-time (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:AI-powered threats\, agentic systems\, non-human identities\, a
 nd cloud-native architectures have rewritten the rules of access governanc
 e at a rapid pace. Identity has moved from a technical function to a strat
 egic imperative — and CISOs are being asked to lead that transformation 
 while simultaneously defending against an escalating wave of sophisticated
  attacks. The organizations that will thrive aren't necessarily the ones w
 ith the most advanced tooling. They're the ones with the clearest thinking
  about risk\, governance\, and the human decisions behind every access con
 trol policy.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4009
 748\n\nSpeakers: Cedric Leighton (CNN Military Analyst\; U.S. Air Force (R
