UID:identiverse-2026-event-4067373@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260615T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260615T191500
SUMMARY:Tech Theater Presented by Rippling: Compliant by Design: Diving int
 o the Security Features Developed by Rippling IT (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Rippling IT enables organizations to manage the entire user lif
 ecycle within a single\, unified platform. By combining identity managemen
 t\, application access\, and device management\, we eliminate the need for
  fragmented tools and manual processes. With over 600 integrations\, inclu
 ding support for custom SCIM and SAML\, teams can seamlessly connect their
  systems and automate provisioning across their tech stack.\nThrough polic
 y-driven automation\, organizations can enforce consistent rules for provi
 sioning\, single sign-on (SSO)\, permissions\, and device management\, red
 ucing risk while improving operational efficiency. One of the features we 
 get most excited about is the ability to deploy custom security policies b
 ased on real-time user and device attributes\, such as department\, role\,
  or operating system. These policies automatically scale across the organi
 zation\, ensuring that access and security controls remain aligned with ch
 anging conditions.\nAll of these features are complimented by our enterpri
 se-grade security capabilities paired with continuous auditing to provide 
 visibility and assurance. The result is a streamlined\, secure\, and scala
 ble approach to managing users\, devices\, and access—all in one place.\
 n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4067373\n\nSessio
 n Type: TECH THEATER\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-
 7)
LOCATION:Tech Theater 3
