SUMMARY:NHAI Pavilion Presented by Descope: Tackling the Identity Alphabet 
 Soup of NHI\, M2M\, and MCP (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Machine identities have always been around\, but the rise of ag
 entic AI and MCP has introduced several challenges and questions for ident
 ity leaders. Are AI agents just another type of machine identity that shou
 ld be governed accordingly? Are API key and OAuth based flows sufficient t
 o secure all machine identities? This session will cover emerging challeng
 es with machine identity\, highlight where AI agents and machine identitie
 s are alike and differ\, and share practical tips to help organizations im
 plement secure identity and credential management for all types of machine
  identities\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=41879
 70\n\nSession Type: NON-HUMAN & AI IDENTITY PAVILION\n\nAll times are in P
