SUMMARY:Mastering Digital Identity Book Signing (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Executives don’t usually think about identity until something
  goes wrong: fraud\, account takeover\, regulatory scrutiny\, or a sudden 
 loss of customer trust. In our AI-accelerated world\, that’s already too
  late. Mastering Digital Identity: From Risk to Revenue by Eve Maler shows
  you how (and why) identity is really your business model in disguise. Thi
 s is an exclusive opportunity to connect\, learn\, and interact. Eve is av
 ailable to sign copies\; approximately 100 books will be available to atte
 ndees on a first come\, first served basis\, courtesy of Cyber1Armor.\n\nD
 etails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4212814\n\nSpeakers: 
 Eve Maler (President/Founder • Venn Factory)\n\nSession Type: NETWORKING
