SUMMARY:Power Breakfast Presented by NewCore Identity: The Identity Stack H
 as a Security Debt. AI Just Called It In (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Every major breach of the last decade ran through identity. Tha
 t's not coincidence - it's an architectural confession. Decades of shortcu
 ts\, fragmented directories\, and stop-gap controls have built a security 
 debt most organizations haven't fully priced. Then AI called it in. AI age
 nts create and dissolve identities in seconds\, moving across systems at m
 achine speed with no human in the loop. Existing infrastructure and guardr
 ails weren't built for this. And more\, quantum computing is already press
 uring the protocols beneath. Legacy cryptography\, the foundation of every
  identity platform\, is running out of runway. Security-first identity arc
 hitecture isn't optional anymore. It's overdue.\n\nDetails: https://identi
 verse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4134855\n\nSession Type: POWER BREAKFAST\n\
 nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
