SUMMARY:Leading a Mission-Driven Identity Culture with Vikas Mahajan (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:As VP and CISO at the American Red Cross\, Vikas Mahajan faces 
 a unique challenge: protecting an infrastructure designed to deliver criti
 cal services\, from disaster response to blood drives\, while supporting a
 nd empowering tens of thousands of external volunteers. To align with its 
 mission\, the Red Cross's security and identity strategies must be uniquel
 y fluid and agile\, while simultaneously pursuing identity modernization a
 nd resiliency. Vikas will diagram his strategies for this balancing act an
 d explain how to find the sweet spot between theory and security.\n\nDetai
 ls: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4005708\n\nSpeakers: Vika
 s Mahajan (Vice President & CISO • American Red Cross)\n\nSession Type: 
 KEYNOTE\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
