SUMMARY:Identity Basics: The Foundation of Secure Access (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:In today’s digital landscape\, identity is the new perimeter.
  Managing and securing identities has become critical to protecting sensit
 ive data and ensuring compliance. This session introduces the fundamentals
  of identity management. We’ll explore why identity is central to modern
  security strategies\, common challenges\, and best practices for implemen
 ting an identity program. Whether you’re new to identity concepts or loo
 king to strengthen your security posture\, this presentation will provide 
 practical insights to help you safeguard your organization’s most valuab
 le asset—its people.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?
 idvid=3964026\n\nSpeakers: Angie Klein (IAM Manager • Federated Insuranc
 e)\n\nSession Type: MASTERCLASS\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time 
 (PDT / UTC-7)
