SUMMARY:Architecting the Agentic AI Identity Security Platform (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:The future is what we make of it. But it’s based upon the rea
 lity of today. This 50-minute Masterclass examines the state of identity s
 ecurity for AI today and explores where it’s headed. We’ll first cover
  real-world examples and use cases\, along with best practices and tips fo
 r governing AI identities.\nThen\, we’ll dive into what’s on the horiz
 on: how to be prepared for what’s next — and keep your organization se
 cure — while adapting your current program for the current iteration of 
 agentic AI and its next evolution.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: http
 s://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4056126\n\nSpeakers: Vibhuti Sinh
 a (Chief Product Officer • Saviynt) | Vinit Shah (Sr. VP\, Product Manag
 ement • Saviynt\, Inc)\n\nSession Type: MASTERCLASS\n\nAll times are in 
 Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
