SUMMARY:Power Lunch Presented by Okta: Okta Secures AI: The Identity Bluepr
 int for the Secure Agentic Enterprise (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:The rise of AI agents is creating new attack paths—are your d
 efenses ready? Join this essential Lunch and Learn to discover why AI secu
 rity is fundamentally identity security. Many organizations are reporting 
 security incidents and failing to treat agents as distinct\, identity-bear
 ing entities. You will walk away with the practical blueprint for a secure
  agentic enterprise and see how Okta helps solve these issues. We will det
 ail how to answer critical questions: Where are my agents? What can they c
 onnect to? What can they do? Learn about vital security components like ag
 ent lifecycle management\, runtime enforcement\, vaulted credentials\, and
  the 'Human-in-the-Loop' kill switch.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/
 idv26/session/?idvid=4086815\n\nSession Type: POWER LUNCH\n\nAll times are
  in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
