  Fabric (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Modern environments need to nify human and machine identity man
 agement. Ultimately\, this is the weaving of a new identity fabric. This u
 nified\, modular architectural framework integrates disparate Identity and
  Access Management (IAM) tools\, policies\, and systems into a cohesive\, 
 centralized structure. Learn how to: - Treat machine identities like human
  identities - Continuously use identity data to verify and provision - Bui
 ld a better baseline and reporting for governance and compliance\n\nDetail
 s: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4076643\n\nSession Type: T
