SUMMARY:Tech Theater Presented by TransUnion: Agentic AI Meets Identity: Bu
 ilding a Self Defending Digital Ecosystem with Device\, Identity & Behavio
 ral Intelligence (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:As agentic AI transforms the identity landscape\, organizations
  must evolve from static fraud controls to dynamic\, autonomous defenses. 
 In this session\, we’ll explore how TransUnion’s Device Risk\, Identit
 y\, and Behavioral Intelligence capabilities serve as core signals that em
 power safer AI‑driven identity flows. We’ll show how agentic AI system
 s can leverage cross‑signal intelligence—device reputation\, identity 
 verification\, behavioral signals\, and risk analytics—to continuously a
 ssess trust\, detect anomalies in real time\, and autonomously reduce fric
 tion for legitimate users. Attendees will learn how combining these signal
 s enables a self‑defending identity ecosystem that anticipates threats\,
  elevates decision accuracy\, and strengthens digital trust across the cus
 tomer journey.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=40
