SUMMARY:NHAI Pavilion Presented by SailPoint: Securing Agents: Discover\, G
 overn\, and Control AI Before the Audit (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Organizations are rapidly deploying AI agents\, but the pace of
  adoption is outstripping the speed of security frameworks. You cannot wai
 t for regulations to set the rules of engagement before securing this dyna
 mic non-human workforce. To safely govern AI before the audit\, enterprise
  security leaders must establish immediate\, foundational control over the
 ir agentic identities. This session delivers a practical blueprint to brid
 ge the AI visibility gap. We will tackle the core pillars of agent identit
 y security by answering the four critical questions every organization mus
 t address: Discover: What AI agents are actually operating in your environ
 ment? Visibility: Who ultimately owns the actions and outcomes of these ag
 ents? Governance: What specific access and permissions do these agents hol
 d? Response: How quickly can you remove access that poses a risk or is no 
 longer required? Join us to learn how to build a proactive governance prog
 ram that empowers your organization to innovate securely\, staying ahead o
 f emerging risks and evolving legislation.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse
 .com/idv26/session/?idvid=4216658\n\nSession Type: NON-HUMAN & AI IDENTITY
  PAVILION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
