SUMMARY:Tech Theater Presented by Ory: Beyond the Human Perimeter: Building
  Identity for Agents\, Customers\, and B2B Scale (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Identity has evolved from a simple login box to the core fabric
  of modern infrastructure. Yet\, as organizations deploy agentic AI and sc
 ale global B2B ecosystems\, legacy\, rigid IAM platforms have become the p
 rimary bottleneck. Teams are often trapped between SaaS-only silos and bri
 ttle architectures unable to handle the speed and scale of autonomous agen
 ts.\nIn this session\, we explore the Identity for Builders philosophy—a
  shift toward API-first\, composable identity that treats AI agents\, B2B 
 partners\, and global customers as first-class citizens. We move past blac
 k box IAM\, demonstrating how modular architecture allows developers to em
 bed identity anywhere—with the freedom to host on-premises\, in the clou
 d\, or as a managed service.\nAttendees will learn:\nThe Blueprint for Age
 nt IAM: Architecting identity for autonomous actors requiring real-time au
 thorization without human intervention.\nComposability as Strategy: How he
 adless IAM eliminates technical debt and enables rapid adaptation to new A
 I threats.\nB2B & CIAM at Scale: Strategies for managing complex multi-ten
 ancy and high-volume traffic without sacrificing sovereignty.\nDeployment 
 Sovereignty: Why hosting flexibility is critical for compliance and low-la
 tency AI workflows.\nWe conclude with a first look at Ory’s Agent IAM ca
 pabilities\, showing how to unify human and agentic workflows under a sing
 le\, high-performance plane.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/ses
 sion/?idvid=4134950\n\nSession Type: TECH THEATER\n\nAll times are in Paci
 fic Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Tech Theater 1
