SUMMARY:Tech Theater Presented by Incode: How AI Agents Are About to Break 
 Identity Security\, and What Can We Do (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:AI agents are quickly becoming a primary user class in digital 
 ecosystems. They authenticate\, execute transactions\, and interact with s
 ervices on behalf of humans and organizations\, but unlike human users\, A
 I agents all look exactly the same - there are no signals such as devices\
 , networks\, locations\, biometrics or other things that help us protect h
 umans.\nThis creates a new identity challenge. If agents cannot be secured
  through conventional signals\, how can organizations determine whether an
  agent is legitimate or malicious?\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv
 26/session/?idvid=4067375\n\nSession Type: TECH THEATER\n\nAll times are i
 n Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
