SUMMARY:Tech Theater Presented by Carahsoft: I Know Why your IGA Implementa
 tion is Failing... (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Abstract: I Know Why Your IGA Program Is FailingYour IGA platfo
 rm is configured correctly. Your engineers are talented. Your policies are
  documented. And yet your application onboarding backlog is measured in ye
 ars\, your application owners dread every interaction with your team\, and
  your CISO just got another audit finding.The problem isn't your technolog
 y. It's your vocabulary.ICAM professionals speak a language the rest of th
 e enterprise doesn't — and most never will. When your team asks an appli
 cation owner for their "SAML assertion attribute mapping\," they disengage
 . Not because they don't care about security\, but because you've handed t
 hem a form written in a foreign language.This session draws on real-world 
 experience managing IGA programs at scale — including environments with 
 multi-thousand application backlogs and millions of managed identities —
  to make the case that the single biggest accelerant to any identity progr
 am is a better translation layer\, not a better tool.\n\nDetails: https://
 identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4067442\n\nSession Type: TECH THEATER
 \n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
