SUMMARY:The Identity Playbook for the Agentic Enterprise (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Every AI security conversation right now starts with gateways a
 nd guardrails. This session skips the buzzwords and looks at what identity
  teams are actually doing: how leading enterprises are moving from AI iden
 tity chaos to an executive-backed strategy. We'll cover how to rationalize
  the non-human and agent identity landscape you already have\, prioritize 
 controls against your own policies\, and extend governance into agentic ac
 cess — without bolting on another tool. You'll leave knowing where ident
 ity fits in your AI security stack\, and exactly where the gateway stops a
 nd identity has to take over.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://i
 dentiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4067370\n\nSpeakers: Adam Ochayon (Dir
 ector\, Product Strategy & GTM • Oasis Security\, Inc.)\n\nSession Type:
  SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Breakers J
