BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:identiverse-2026-event-3931794@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260616T143500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260616T150000
SUMMARY:Passkeys at PayPal - Learnings\, Best Practices and Beyond! (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:In this talk\, I will share PayPal's comprehensive journey of d
 eploying FIDO-based passkey authentication across its sites and platforms\
 , reaching millions of customers globally. We will delve into the various 
 options we implemented\, the challenges we faced during the large-scale ro
 llout\, and the best practices we established to ensure a smooth transitio
 n.\nImplementation Options:We will discuss the different FIDO-based soluti
 ons we considered and ultimately adopted\, highlighting factors like platf
 orm compatibility\, user experience\, and security considerations.Challeng
 es and Solutions:We will openly share the challenges we encountered during
  deployment\, such as user adoption\, integration complexities\, and legac
 y system compatibility. We will then delve into the solutions we implement
 ed to overcome these hurdles\, providing insights valuable to organization
 s contemplating similar deployments.Best Practices:We will outline the bes
 t practices we established throughout the process\, encompassing areas lik
 e user education\, communication strategies\, and ongoing maintenance. The
 se practices have proven instrumental in ensuring a successful and secure 
 passwordless authentication experience for our vast user base.Evolving Str
 ategy:We will explore how our initial deployment strategy evolved as we ga
 ined experience and user feedback. This will share valuable insights into 
 adapting strategies to address unforeseen challenges and maximize user ado
 ption.Global Impact:We will showcase the positive impact of our FIDO passk
 ey deployment on millions of users worldwide. This will include improved s
 ecurity\, streamlined login experiences\, and increased user confidence in
  online interactions.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?i
 dvid=3931794\n\nSpeakers: Mahendar Madhavan (Director of Product\, Identit
 y • PayPal) | Walmik Deshpande (Architect\, Identity Experiences • Pay
 Pal) | Mohit Ganotra (Principal Product Manager • PayPal)\n\nSession Typ
 e: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Mandalay Bay F
