UID:identiverse-2026-event-4056440@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260616T143500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260616T150000
SUMMARY:The Ghost in the Machine (Securing Non-Human Identities) (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Non-human identities are the ghost in the machine. Whether we a
 re discussing service accounts or artificial intelligence\, visibility\, p
 rivileged access\, governance\, and risk mitigation are becoming the lates
 t attack vectors dominating breaches. In this presentation\, we will discu
 ss the rise of non-human identities\, flaws in design and management of po
 licies\, and the specter elevating risk – AI. For attendees\, you will l
 earn how solutions\, policies\, and best practices can mitigate risks and 
 wrangle in the ghost in your machines.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: 
 https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4056440\n\nSpeakers: Morey Ha
 ber (Chief Security Advisor • BeyondTrust)\n\nSession Type: SESSION\n\nA
 ll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Breakers L
