SUMMARY:Inside Identity @ PlayStation: Strategies for Modern Consumer Threa
 ts (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:As passkeys have strengthened authentication\, the most challen
 ging identity problems have shifted well beyond sign-in. In this session\,
  PlayStation’s Product and Security teams explore what drives consumer a
 ccount takeover while highlighting the tactics attackers use across our di
 verse player and platform ecosystem. We will show how real-world threat in
 sights shape our strategic approach to modern identity challenges in the c
 onsumer space. Topics include device identification\, persistent authentic
 ation\, and account recovery\, with a focus on balancing strong security w
 ith smooth\, intuitive player experiences that support trust\, retention\,
  and long-term business growth.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/
 session/?idvid=3931744\n\nSpeakers: Cam Champeau (Senior Product Manager 
 • Sony Interactive Entertainment (PlayStation)) | Grant Walthall (Staff 
 Application Security Analyst • Sony Interactive Entertainment (PlayStati
 on))\n\nSession Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (P
 DT / UTC-7)
