SUMMARY:The Identity Security AI Metamorphosis (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:AI has thrown open the doors for today's enterprises. It's chan
 ged how (and with whom) we work\, accelerating workflows and completing ta
 sks faster than humans could ever dream. Its practicality in identity secu
 rity is certain\, but for most identity professionals\, not yet fully expl
 ored.This session explores AI's place and function in identity security\, 
 from drastically reducing time-to-value on key processes such as app onboa
 rding\, intelligently automating tedious tasks like access requests and ce
 rtifications\, or reducing the time it takes for audit preparedness and ev
 idence collection. Learn from real-world examples of those who've implemen
 ted AI for identity security so you can do the same in your organization.\
 n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4138061\n\nSpeake
 rs: Nupur Goyal (VP Product Marketing • Saviynt) | Gnana Thanikachalam (
 Senior Director • Hertz Global Holdings Inc)\n\nSession Type: SESSION\n\
 nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
