DESCRIPTION:As agentic AI reshapes enterprise systems\, identity becomes th
 e foundation for trust\, control\, and scale. In this session\, Jose Rodri
 guez and Grant Miller share how IBM operationalized Agentic Identity acros
 s a global enterprise using IBM Verify as Client Zero. Learn how real-worl
 d deployment informed architecture\, policy\, and governance decisions—t
 urning product vision into scalable\, production-ready identity for humans
 \, machines\, and AI agents.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://id
 entiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4142053\n\nSpeakers: Jose Rodriguez (Di
 stinguished Engineer Identity and Access Management - Chief Product Archit
