BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:identiverse-2026-event-3964042@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260616T163000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260616T165500
SUMMARY:More Than Who You Are: The Role of Intent in Digital Identity (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Identity used to be simple. A username\, a password\, maybe a d
 evice.\nBut today\, identity spans dozens of ecosystems: cloud\, mobile\, 
 web\, tablet\, IoT\, biometrics\, delegated AI.\nStatic identity attribute
 s are no longer enough. They don’t express behavior\, context\, or motiv
 ation.\nAnd attackers exploit this\, they mimic attributes at the perimete
 r.\nWhat they cannot easily copy is intent and the holistic journey the cu
 stomer has taken over time.\nWe need identity systems that can answer:\nWh
 o is my user?\nWhat did the user do?What do they normally do?Why did they 
 do it?\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=3964042\n\
 nSpeakers: David Bailey (Sr Dir\, Fraud Prevention & Solutions • TIAA)\n
 \nSession Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / U
 TC-7)
LOCATION:Mandalay Bay K
CLASS:PUBLIC
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
