SUMMARY:Tech Theater Presented by Lumos: Defending AI Agents With AI Agents
 : A Practical Guide for a Post-Mythos World (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:What happens when human-centric identity meets an agentic workf
 orce that never sleeps\, scales instantly\, and doesn’t follow process? 
 In this new reality\, visibility and intelligence fall short unless archit
 ected to scale alongside the agentic workforce.\nThis session examines how
  traditional identity systems fail when forced to manage both human and no
 n-human actors and what leading organizations do differently.\nLearn how o
 rganizations:\nDetect and remediate identity security risks\, enforce leas
 t privilege\, and drive scalable governance for all types of identities\nS
 cale core identity functions like access reviews\, provisioning\, roles\, 
 entitlements\, policies\, and audits with agents.\nSupport AI and automati
 on initiatives without increasing identity-related risk.\n\nDetails: https
