 assing it by targeting the human workflows around identity. Help desk acco
 unt recovery and remote hiring processes have become prime entry points fo
 r impersonation\, account takeover\, and workforce infiltration.\nLearn ab
 out workforce identity verification and how to detect attacker-controlled 
 environments and confirm the legitimacy of the employee during critical li
 fecycle moments like hiring\, onboarding\, and account recovery. Hear real
 -world examples of how to stop impersonation before credentials are issued
