SUMMARY:The New Frontier of Identity Security for AI (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:In just 2 years\, the number of AI identities is expected to re
 ach 1.3 billion — about 1/7th of the world's population. Yet the majorit
 y of organizations today don't govern AI identities in a way that keeps th
 em secure\, giving access far beyond what's required and following process
 es both ancient and slow.What organizations are left with are massive gaps
  in agent access visibility\, ownership & governance\, and policies that a
 lways enforce the right principles. Join Saviynt CEO and Co-Founder\, Sach
 in Nayyar\, and our guest CISO to learn about the challenges of — and so
 lutions for — identity security for AI.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.
 com/idv26/session/?idvid=4005713\n\nSpeakers: Sachin Nayyar (Founder & CEO
  • Saviynt\,Inc.) | Jamil Farshchi (Chief Technology Officer • Equifax
 )\n\nSession Type: KEYNOTE\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT 
 / UTC-7)
