SUMMARY:Hacking Agentic AI: Live Attack\, Exploit and Identity-Driven Defen
 se (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Agentic AI is already in your environment and it’s likely ove
 r-privileged\, under-governed\, and exposed.\nIn this session\, we hack an
  AI agent live - abusing identities\, tokens\, and APIs to escalate access
  and trigger unintended actions. And then we stop it!\nWatch how a layered
  IAM model: PAM for machine identities\, access controls for API enforceme
 nt\, and IGA for visibility and cleanup together contain the blast radius.
 \nSee what works\, where gaps exist\, and how to secure agentic AI without
  slowing it down.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.c
 om/idv26/session/?idvid=4076645\n\nSpeakers: Mohit Vaish (CEO • CyberSol
 ve) | Mak Tomar (SVP - Identity Governance - Service Projects • CyberSol
 ve)\n\nSession Type: MASTERCLASS\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time
