SUMMARY:Who's Watching the Agents? Identity Security in the Age of Autonomo
 us AI (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:We are entering the agentic economy\, where AI\, machine\, and 
 other non-human identities are performing critical tasks and accessing sen
 sitive data at an explosive scale. This creates a new and complex attack s
 urface that traditional security models were not built to handle. This tec
 hnical master class provides a framework for establishing robust governanc
 e over this new workforce. We will dive into best practices for managing a
 gent identity security\, machine identity security\, and data access secur
 ity. Through instructional content and practical examples\, you'll learn h
 ow to discover\, classify\, and secure non-human identities\, enforce leas
 t privilege access\, and build a security architecture for the future of w
 ork.\nGrasp the new security challenges of the agentic economy\nLearn a fr
 amework to discover\, classify\, and secure non-human identities\nUncover 
 how to enforce least privilege for AI agents and machines\nLearn how you c
 an define an agent’s behavior by its access\nSession Presented by:\n\nDe
 tails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4082874\n\nSpeakers: M
 att Fangman (Field CTO • SailPoint)\n\nSession Type: MASTERCLASS\n\nAll 
