 me join Health ISAC for an Identiverse meetup to talk through unique ident
 ity challenges in health care. Over the last 8 years\, Health ISAC has pub
 lished a series of whitepapers for health CISOs on IAM\, with a focus on p
 romoting an identity-centric approach to cybersecurity. At this meetup\, w
 e will talk about some of these papers and explore new and emerging challe
 nges in the health sector.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/sessi
