SUMMARY:The Invisible Workforce: Agentic AI from Risk to Results (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:The rise of agentic AI has introduced a powerful class of auton
 omous\, non-human identities\, an invisible digital workforce that demands
  executive oversight. This panel reframes non-human identity (NHI) governa
 nce from a niche security control into a strategic lever for innovation an
 d growth. Leaders will learn how to bridge business strategy and technical
  risk – securing executive sponsorship\, implementing guardrails that sc
 ale\, and demonstrating tangible ROI. Featuring cross-functional practitio
 ners\, the discussion will unpack what worked (and what didn’t) in align
 ing stakeholders\, implementing governance and controls across technology 
 and process\, and instrumenting the metrics executives care about.\n\nDeta
 ils: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=3931793\n\nSpeakers: Gra
 ce Sands (Director • KPMG LLP) | Katie Boswell (Managing Director • KP
 MG LLP) | Jody Hunt (Senior Solution Strategy Architect • Palo Alto Netw
 orks) | Baber Amin (• Saviynt) | Jake Pszonowsky (VP Security & Identity
 \, Global Technology • Universal Music Group)\n\nSession Type: MASTERCLA
