SUMMARY:Power Lunch Presented by Cisco Duo: Mind the Gap: Identity and Acce
 ss Control for AI Agents (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:There is a trust gap between agent pilots and production. AI ag
 ents are autonomous\; they access enterprise tools and data\, make decisio
 ns\, and act at machine speed. How do you apply identity and access contro
 l to a workforce that isn't human? Join this interactive session to explor
 e these challenges with your peers: identity sprawl\, permission gaps\, be
 havioral drift\, and shadow AI. Using live audience polling\, we'll benchm
 ark where you stand compared to your peers across five themes: agentic use
 \, monitoring\, identity management\, access control\, and runtime behavio
 r. Bring your questions\, your opinions\, and your appetite.\n\nDetails: h
 ttps://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4086814\n\nSession Type: POWER
