SUMMARY:Power Lunch Presented by Vonage: Beyond OTP: How Network APIs Are R
 edefining Trust and Authentication (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Traditional OTP-based two-factor authentication creates frictio
 n and may be susceptible to social engineering attacks. Identity Insights\
 , powered by Network APIs\, allows for user verification through their mob
 ile network operators in seconds—without codes\, without friction.This i
 nteractive conversation explores how this GSMA and Linux Foundation-backed
  standard is transforming digital authentication across financial services
 \, and other verticals. Learn from real-world results: Lydia Bank eliminat
 ed 100% of SMS social engineering attacks while achieving 50% faster authe
 ntication and improved conversion rates. Attendees will discover how to ba
 lance security with seamless user experience\, when to implement Silent Au
 thentication\, and what measurable business outcomes to expect.\n\nDetails
