SUMMARY:Zero-License IAM: Replacing Bloatware with Agentic AI (Live Build &
  Demo) (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Most enterprises use less than half of their IAM capabilities b
 ut pay for the full stack. The result: bloatware\, rigid processes\, and h
 igh costs.\nWhat if you didn’t need the platform at all?\nIn this live b
 uild and demo\, we deconstruct IAM into core functions: JML\, access reque
 sts\, authentication and authorization\, certifications\, and then rebuild
  them using agentic AI. See how workflows\, provisioning\, and access deci
 sions are dynamically generated without a monolithic product.\nWe’ll als
 o cover where this works\, where it doesn’t\, and how to adopt it withou
 t setting up an AI engineering team.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: ht
 tps://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4076648\n\nSpeakers: Eugert Jan
 i (Senior Director of Access Management • CyberSolve) | Mak Tomar (SVP -
  Identity Governance - Service Projects • CyberSolve)\n\nSession Type: S
 ESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
