SUMMARY:Accelerate Incident Response: Why Identity is the Missing Link in Y
 our SOC (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Your identity platform is a goldmine of real-time security sign
 als. It sees every access request\, every change in privilege\, and every 
 login—often the earliest indicators of an attack. But without the right 
 context\, these valuable signals become just more noise contributing to th
 e alert fatigue already crippling most Security Operations Centers (SOCs).
  Traditional security tools lack the one piece of context that matters mos
 t: identity. Without knowing who is behind an event\, it's nearly impossib
 le to distinguish a real threat from a false alarm. This session will expl
 ore the critical importance of integrating identity insights directly into
  your security operations. We will discuss how access to identity context 
 can dramatically accelerate threat detection\, streamline incident respons
 e\, and enable proactive risk mitigation. Learn how to empower your SOC to
  move from a reactive to a predictive stance by harnessing identity intell
 igence.\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4082869\n
 \nSpeakers: Jonas Outlaw (Principal Product Manager • SailPoint)\n\nSess
 ion Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Breakers H
