SUMMARY:Liminal Demo Day (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:The Ultimate High-Signal Product Showcase\nAs the identity mark
 et matures\, enterprise buyers are moving past "thought leadership" to see
 k clear\, practical evaluations of real solutions. Liminal Demo Day is a 6
 0-minute\, sponsor-exclusive session designed to meet this demand. We’ve
  stripped away the marketing fluff to create a focused\, high-intensity en
 vironment where the product does the talking.\nThe "No-Slide" Challenge: W
 e’ve replaced traditional presentations with a structured\, competitive 
 demonstration format. This is about live performance\, not slide decks.\n8
 -Minute In-person Demos. Zero PowerPoint: No slides. No corporate overview
 s. Just the interface\, the workflow\, and the solution.\nThe "3-Lens" Fee
 dback Panel: Every demo is immediately followed by a live Q&A and critique
  from a panel representing the full buyer journey:\nThe Investor: Evaluati
 ng market viability and long-term scalability.\nThe Practitioner: Testing 
 for real-world integration and operational friction.\nThe Market Analyst: 
 Mapping the solution against broader industry trends.\nJudges:\nLevgeniia 
 Zhovtobriukh\, Group Project Manager\, Google Kelley Hilborn\, Vice Presid
 ent\, Mosaic\, KeyBank Travis Jarae CEO\, Liminal\nParticipating Sponsors:
 \n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4188294\n\nSpeak
 ers: Akshay Srinivas Rajanbabu (Distinguished Engineer\, Solution Consulti
 ng • Radiant Logic) | Rich Eisenberg (VP of Client Development • Unixi
 ) | Aaron Keisler (Senior Software Engineer • P0 Security) | Raj Galagal
 i (VP\, Global Solutions Engineering • Transmit Security)\n\nSession Typ
 e: LIMINAL DEMO DAY\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7
 )
