SUMMARY:Identity Tips to Improve User Onboarding and Conversion (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Customer identity can make your business tick or stall. Login f
 riction\, cumbersome MFA\, identity silos\, and legacy APIs can be the dif
 ference between a lifelong customer and a dropoff. This session will cover
  learnings from real-world deployments and highlight how passwordless auth
 entication\, guest checkout\, adaptive MFA\, and agentic identity can prov
 ide frictionless user experiences without sacrificing security.\nSession P
 resented by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4117
 126\n\nSpeakers: Rishi Bhargava (Co-Founder • Descope)\n\nSession Type: 
