 ow do you centralize identity infrastructure across dozens of franchises w
 hile preserving each team’s distinct brand\, digital experience\, and fa
 n loyalty? In this session\, Michael Wachell from the NFL will share how t
 hey architected a multi-brand customer identity strategy that balances cen
 tralized governance with decentralized brand autonomy.\nSession Presented 
 by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4184118\n\nSp
