SUMMARY:Rethinking Identity Security — For Innovation\, Confidence\, and 
 AI (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:For the past few decades\, we’ve built cybersecurity systems 
 based on human rules. Meanwhile\, we dreamed of how machine learning and A
 I would revolutionize the world. But when our dreams finally came to fruit
 ion and AI became part of our everyday\, the reality of our designed-for-h
 umans processes and systems showed us all that we hadn’t thought of.\nTo
 day\, identity security for AI is perhaps the most important undertaking f
 or identity professionals. But what does identity security for AI agents a
 ctually look like? How do you implement it? In this session\, we’ll disc
 uss best practices and use cases so you can walk away with real next steps
  for your own organization.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://ide
 ntiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4056117\n\nSpeakers: Vibhuti Sinha (Chie
 f Product Officer • Saviynt) | Ajitha Choudar (VP\, Global Security Engi
 neering & IAM • UKG)\n\nSession Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacifi
 c Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Mandalay Bay D
