 T)
DESCRIPTION:Discover how Vanguard achieved phishing resistance and advanced
  Zero Trust with end to end FIDO2 authentication. This session shares key 
 lessons and best practices to implement hardware-backed security at scale
 —boosting identity protection and reducing cyber risk from AI and phishi
 ng threats.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv
 26/session/?idvid=4137968\n\nSpeakers: Andrew Szajlai (Se Security Archite
 ct • Vanguard) | David Olsen (Sr Director\, Customer Advocacy • Yubico
