SUMMARY:From AI Chaos to Control: Securing Your New Agentic Workforce (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:The rise of AI is transforming business\, but it's also creatin
 g unprecedented security challenges. How can you ensure that the right ide
 ntities have the right access\, right now\, in a constantly shifting digit
 al landscape? This session explores the critical need for an adaptive iden
 tity security strategy\, powered by real-time governance\, to successfully
  navigate today’s agentic economy. We will move beyond traditional\, sta
 tic access controls and discuss a new paradigm where identity security is 
 intelligent\, contextual\, and continuous. Join SailPoint and Equinix to l
 earn how to govern and secure the new agentic workforce\, ensuring your or
 ganization can safely innovate at the speed of the modern enterprise.\nSes
 sion Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvi
 d=4082872\n\nSpeakers: Levent Besik (Chief Product Officer​ • SailPoin
 t) | Vinay Bhonde (Identity Security Leader • Equinix)\n\nSession Type: 
 SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
