SUMMARY:Tips to Simplify B2B2X Identity Complexity (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:In B2B2X environments\, identity sits at the intersection of mu
 ltiple organizations\, applications\, and user groups. As platforms evolve
  to serve customers\, partners\, contractors\, and emerging AI agents\, id
 entity infrastructures must accommodate diverse authentication methods\, t
 enant boundaries\, and governance requirements.\nThis session will cover r
 eal-world deployments in complex B2B2X ecosystems and highlight how multi-
 tenant architectures\, self-service identity administration\, passwordless
  authentication\, and identity federation can address identity challenges 
 within these environments.\nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://iden
 tiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4117127\n\nSpeakers: Rishi Bhargava (Co-F
 ounder • Descope)\n\nSession Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific D
 aylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Breakers J
