BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:identiverse-2026-event-4117180@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260617T163000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260617T165500
SUMMARY:Taming the Wild West of Non-Human Identities\; Bringing Governance 
 and Oversight to the Untamed Digital Frontier (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Non-human identities (NHI) are exploding across the enterprise.
  New types of identities are popping up in every corner of the business an
 d managing non-human identities has become like the wild west. These chall
 enges are compounded by the varying types of non-human identities and the 
 fundamental truth that not all Non-Human Identities are created equal. Tam
 ing the frontier of Non-Human Identities requires a nuanced approach to go
 vernance\; assigning the right security and control framework to the right
  set of identities. Join us for a conversation around the new and evolving
  set of Non-Human Identities\, how Non-Human Identities still require a la
 yer of human oversight\, and how different identity technologies are tryin
 g to bring some law and order to the Non-Human identity landscape.\nSessio
 n Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4
 117180\n\nSpeakers: Ben Wise (VP of Identity Management • IDMWORKS)\n\nS
