SUMMARY:Accelerate your Identity Security for Modern Identity Defense (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Identity is the foundation of modern security\, the most target
 ed layer in any environment\, and the first line of defense. Protecting a 
 growing ecosystem of human users\, non-human identities\, and AI agents ha
 s become mission-critical.\nIn this session\, we will share how a unified 
 approach to identity security brings together Identity and Access Manageme
 nt (IAM) and Security Operations (SOC) to secure any identity\, anywhere. 
 Learn how to build a more resilient identity fabric against modern attacks
  by securing your identity infrastructure\, hardening your identity postur
 e\, and empowering real-time access decisions\, and extending autonomous d
 etection and response across your entire identity footprint.\nSession Pres
 ented by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4138062
 \n\nSpeakers: Jared Ross (Product Architect • Microsoft)\n\nSession Type
 : SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
