UID:identiverse-2026-event-4082873@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260617T170500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260617T173000
SUMMARY:Stop Building Identity Plumbing. Start Scaling Secure Agents. (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:Your CIAM secures user access\, but the agentic era demands som
 ething new: securing agents acting on behalf of users at machine speed. Tr
 aditional identity wasn't built for autonomous workflows where agents exec
 ute trades\, approve loans\, and access sensitive data constantly.This ses
 sion is for architects\, developers\, and identity leaders building produc
 tion AI.\nYou'll learn how to secure the entire agent journey:\nVerified I
 ntent: Every agent action traces back to a verified human\nScoped Credenti
 als: Token Vault replaces god-keys with ephemeral\, task-specific access\n
 Permission-Aware Data: FGA ensures agents only access authorized rows—wh
 ether 10 or 10 million\nStandardized Tools: Auth for MCP secures agent-to-
 tool connections across 150+ appsSee real patterns: trading agents that ca
 n't exceed authority limits\, loan agents that only see assigned customers
 \, compliance agents with read-only access.Leave with a blueprint to deplo
 y production-grade AI in weeks—secure\, scalable\, and compliant by desi
 gn. Stop building plumbing. Start shipping features.\nSession Presented by
 :\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=4082873\n\nSpea
 kers: Mira Sharma (Product Manager\, Auth0 for AI agents • Okta)\n\nSess
 ion Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
LOCATION:Breakers L
