UID:identiverse-2026-event-4191301@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260617T170500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260617T173000
SUMMARY:Runtime Identity: Trust at the Speed of AI (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:AI agents are about to outnumber humans 80 to 1\, chaining toge
 ther and making decisions at speeds humans simply can't match\, in ways tr
 aditional identity stacks were never built to handle. Whether through shad
 ow IT\, personal agent usage\, or top-down mandates\, organizations are ad
 opting agents\, with or without a trust model that can keep up.\nThis sess
 ion introduces Runtime Identity\, a new model for trusting agents in motio
 n. Join Ping and eBay to learn how to build an architecture that moves bey
 ond impersonation\, over-privilege\, and static access to one grounded in 
 agent discovery and governance\, delegation\, and transaction-level dynami
 c authorization. Get your photo app ready\, you'll want to snap pictures h
 ere to showcase how your business can architect trust at the speed of AI.\
 nSession Presented by:\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?
 idvid=4191301\n\nSpeakers: Brian Yoon (Senior Vice President\, Solutions A
 rchitecture • Ping Identity) | Tanu Kaushik (Sr. Manager\, IAM • eBay)
 \n\nSession Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacific Daylight Time (PDT /
  UTC-7)
LOCATION:Breakers J
