BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:identiverse-2026-event-3931665@identiverse.com
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260612T220134Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260618T094000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260618T100500
SUMMARY:Welcome to the Identity Tribe: Tips & Tricks for Designing your Own
  Customer‑First Career in Digital Identity (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:So you don't have a degree in IT? Don't panic\, you still belon
 g here!Discover the excitement of a career in customer digital identity\, 
 where every day is a chance to innovate and make a real impact. As a Senio
 r Product Manager\, I’ve tackled fraud threats\, pioneered age verificat
 ion\, and represented my team at global conferences—all while driving cu
 stomer-focused solutions in a rapidly evolving industry. This session will
  share practical tips for graduates and newcomers: how to turn challenges 
 into opportunities\, build strong networks\, and lead with confidence. Lea
 rn how digital identity offers a fast-paced\, rewarding path where your wo
 rk shapes the future of trust and security online. If you want a career th
 at’s dynamic\, meaningful\, and never boring\, this talk is for you.\n\n
 Details: https://identiverse.com/idv26/session/?idvid=3931665\n\nSpeakers:
  Linden Dawson (Customer Digital Identity\, Senior Product Manager • Nat
