SUMMARY:Intuit’s Journey: Unifying Workload Identity Across Heterogeneous
  Cloud Environments (PDT)
DESCRIPTION:As cloud environments fracture into heterogeneous landscapes\, 
 managing machine identity becomes a critical security bottleneck. This ses
 sion details Intuit’s journey deploying a unified workload identity fram
 ework across diverse public cloud and on-premise infrastructures.We will e
 xamine the architectural transition from static secrets to short-lived\, c
 ryptographically verifiable identities\, highlighting the specific challen
 ges of interoperability and scale. Attendees will gain a transparent view 
 of the technical hurdles\, cultural shifts\, and security wins achieved du
 ring this massive deployment. Join us to obtain a proven roadmap for imple
 menting Zero Trust principles for workloads without compromising engineeri
 ng velocity or developer experience\n\nDetails: https://identiverse.com/id
 v26/session/?idvid=3931736\n\nSpeakers: Dmitry Izumskiy (Principal Softwar
 e Architect • Intuit)\n\nSession Type: SESSION\n\nAll times are in Pacif
 ic Daylight Time (PDT / UTC-7)
